title._content: Rolling Hills in the Outskirts of Atchison, Kansas, Showing an Area of Landscape Painted by George Catlin between 1830 and 1850...06/1974

description._content: Original Caption: Rolling Hills in the Outskirts of Atchison, Kansas, Showing an Area of Landscape Painted by George Catlin between 1830 and 1850. It Once Was Tallgrass Prairie as Described in the Lewis and Clark Jourals.
